{"tid":1057596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業生校門外拍照遭老師報警趕走 聖保祿中學終致歉","createTime":"2019-03-12T03:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T08:08:59.000Z","uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6ecf510187eeb608d8914de09b7ac0a35d3e6430","tid":1057596,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"跑馬地女校聖保祿中學在中六生最後上課日當天（2月28日），報警驅趕在校門前拍照的畢業生，事後校方指因有老師擔心學生安全，情急之下而私下報警求助。事件引起學生不滿，要求校方處分涉事老師，有舊生更發聲明斥校方謊話連篇，並發起聯署，要求與校方討論將來同類事件的處理手法等。校方一直堅拒道歉，但昨日（11日）終「跪低」，就事件發聲明道歉。<br />\n<br />\n聖保祿中學以題為「中六學生最後上課日事件」，在學校網頁發聲明指，為事件引致各方困擾、不安，衷心致歉。校方又指，會全面檢視學校各項活動的安排，確保日後更能妥善處理。而相關老師對倉卒報警一事，亦深表歉意。<br />\n<br />\n聖保祿中學上周五（8日）補鑊，開放班房供中六生回校影相，但有中六生坦言「已經返唔到去嗰一日嘅感覺，永遠都係我哋記憶入面，學校做咩都補救唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n太遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fc92a913134db71b1ebea3cf1ac598603f8a91","tid":1057596,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34qKUFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34qKUFB.png&h=ebdffb31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28d207682b07be6384c2d9b8277c0dbac77330f3","tid":1057596,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190312/59358793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59358793&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6PrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=3a9a63c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59358793&h=174e15a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190312/59358793</a>"},{"pid":"adfc52bafd9ec1efdb8a72fbed069aba29a26592","tid":1057596,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03: